extendedInfo.description: NOTE:  NOT A RADIO PLAYER.  This app currently doesn't enable auto-starting the FM Radio app, yet.  For now it's a radio station finder.FindFM helps you find local radio stations that suit your taste! Local radio stations appear as soon as you open the app. Tapping the stars next to radio stations lets us know what your favorite stations are. After you pick a few favorites, stations that broadcast similar content will show up at the top of the list, wherever you go! Finds both AM and FM.  Perfect for roadtrips!Zip Codes in Puerto Rico should work now.  Enjoy!
